    "As machine-learning based systems, to achieve high accuracy, ASAG engines MethodologyThe SciEntSBank and BEEtlE datasets [7] were downloaded from kaggle [28].",
    "They included both training and test data.",
    "The training data were discarded, while the test data included the 504 items and 14, 186 student answers and their reference grading that were used for this study.",
    "As no training took place, the distinction between unseen answers (UA), unseen questions (UQ), and unseen domains (UD) that the dataset provided was dropped for this study, since all items were \"unseen.",
